translate portuguese whitney0_24d01809:

    # "I walk down to the basement and check Dad's laptop."
    "Desço até à cave e vejo o portátil do pai."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:13
translate portuguese whitney0_df4af9e8:

    # "There is a reply from Whitney."
    "Há uma resposta da Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:14
translate portuguese whitney0_0e14f5d3:

    # "I take a deep breath and open the e-mail."
    "Respiro fundo e abro o e-mail."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:17
translate portuguese whitney0_7fb0886e:

    # "She would contact me soon, she says."
    "Ela ia contactar-me em breve, diz ela."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:18
translate portuguese whitney0_22c45920:

    # "I guess that's better than nothing. I don't have any other leads right now anyway."
    "Acho que é melhor do que nada. De qualquer forma, não tenho mais nenhuma pista neste momento."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:19
translate portuguese whitney0_0f12dd8e:

    # "I'll just have to wait and hope that she follows through with what she says."
    "Vou ter de esperar e torcer para que ela cumpra o que disse."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:22
translate portuguese whitney0_4373f251:

    # "I send her a quick message back."
    "Respondo-lhe com uma mensagem rápida."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:23
translate portuguese whitney0_606df8e7:

    # "\"I'll wait, but don't take too long.\""
    "«Vou esperar, mas não demores muito.»"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney0.rpy:24
translate portuguese whitney0_d972c5fe:

    # "Then I close the laptop and walk back upstairs."
    "Depois, fecho o portátil e volto para cima."

